/* Armor data: parsed by docstring-json into webapp/data/armor.json
   Armor Attributes (from Weapons & Armor page):
   - Weight: Encumbrance value; adds to non-combat fatigue
   - Signature: TN for Subterfuge checks to conceal the armor
   - Protection: Damage reduction applied to incoming damage
*/
