      </ul>
    """
  },
  "Emergency Shield": {
    "cost": 8000,
    "rarity": 5,
    "weight": 0,
    "signature": 1,
    "flavor": "A palm-sized capacitor bank wired to a thin emitter mesh worn beneath clothing. When struck, it discharges in a fraction of a second, projecting a kinetic barrier capable of stopping a rifle round dead. The charge is good for exactly one hit. A favorite of diplomats, corporate executives, and anyone else who suspects they may need it but would rather not advertise the fact.",
    "description": """
      <h3>Effects</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>The first time the wearer takes damage from any source, reduce that damage to 0. The Emergency Shield immediately gains the <strong>Damaged</strong> quality and cannot trigger again until repaired or replaced.</li>
